name: The Perennial Valley
description:
Those who fall into the Perennial Valley suffer a different kind of horror.
The valley itself is quite small and the way out is clear for all to see, but anyone who tries to reach it will discover that a single step seems to last as long as eternity, though an outsider would see them moving at a normal speed.
Many have managed to escape this land, only to find themselves completely broken by the experience.
As for the rest, they still lay there, experiencing a demise that will last for aeons.
